{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1c749188f5","title":"各国没有明伦堂","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"588df65bf2","index":0,"year":1919,"month":7,"day":14,"articleId":"1c749188f5"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji1","name":"毛泽东全集第1卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji1.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"a9e59ee0e9","type":"paragraph","text":"各国没有明伦堂","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji1","articleId":"1c749188f5"},{"id":"e4fdd66b52","type":"paragraph","text":"（1919年7月14日）康有为因为广州修马路，要折（拆）毁明伦堂，动了肝火打电给岑伍，为“梅圣灭伦”。说：“遍游各国，未之前闻。”康先生的话真不错，遍游各国，那里寻得出什么孔子。更寻不出什么明伦堂。U明伦堂，我国旧时各地孔庙的大段名称。[2]明伦堂，我国旧时各地孔庙的大段名称。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji1","articleId":"1c749188f5"},{"id":"fc90339993","type":"paragraph","text":"岑，指岑春煌（1861-1933），显名春泽，字云阶，广西西林人。曾任北京政府官员，时为广州护法军玫府主房总截。伍，指伍延芳（1842-1922），字文圈，号康，广东新会人，时为广州护法军政府七总规之一，并兼外长和财长。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji1","articleId":"1c749188f5"}],"page":{"id":"19a08ec980","publicationId":"maoquanji1","articleId":"1c749188f5","start":531,"end":531}}}},"__N_SSG":true}